  "description": "Gives boring blocks the building expansions they deserve!",
  "body": "<h2><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hh0aDEH.png\" width=\"655\" height=\"103\" /></h2>\n<p><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Sculpt is a builders expansion mod</strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> which adds versatile block expansions to pre-existing vanilla lacklustre block-sets. It also aims to create consistency within building palettes by adding more cracked chiseled, and wall versions of blocks. The mod will get more blocks as it updates.</span></p>\n<h2><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5gz1HRz.png\" width=\"657\" height=\"103\" /></strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>Versatile block set expansions for boring vanilla blocks </b></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>Calcite, Tuff, Dripstone, Amethyst, Sandstone, Andesite, Granite, Diorite and way more are expanded upon</b></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>More cracked versions of vanilla blocks ( Cracked Prismarine, Mud Bricks, and Bricks )</b></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>More chiseled versions of vanilla blocks ( Chiseled Prismarine, Mud Bricks, and Bricks )</b></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>More Consistency ( Stone walls, Dark prismarine walls &amp; more )</b></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>More blocks to come as the mod updates!</b></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6elVHBo.png\" width=\"656\" height=\"103\" /></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>\"Will Sculpt be back-ported to X version\"</strong></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">No versions behind 1.18.2 will be backported to.</span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>\"Am I allowed to use Sculpt in a modpack?\"</strong></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Of course! credit / a link to the mod would appreciated but is not required.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/puT4msz.png\" width=\"660\" height=\"104\" /><br /></strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>YouTube</strong> can be accessed<span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong> <a style=\"color: #993300;\" title=\"YouTube\" href=\"https://youtube.com/c/muffinsqw\">here</a></strong></span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Community Discord Server</strong> can be joined <span style=\"color: #666699;\"><a style=\"color: #666699;\" title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/Ebcqkp8vpC\">here</a> </span>-- <em>(Join for sneak peaks and support!)</em></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If you'd like to<strong> donate</strong>,&nbsp;my <strong>Ko-Fi</strong> can be accessed <span style=\"color: #ff9900;\"><a style=\"color: #ff9900;\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/muffinsqw\">here</a></span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Use code \"<strong>muffinsqw</strong>\" for 25% off your first Minecraft server at <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/muffinsqw\"><span style=\"color: #00ccff;\">Bisect Hosting</span></a>&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3ZuBUP6.png\" width=\"658\" height=\"103\" /></strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Made using </span><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MCreator</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SxncOs7.png\" width=\"658\" height=\"103\" /></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/muffinsqw\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Enlightened_End/BH_EE_Promo.png\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
